"text-indent: 2.125em;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, " pingfang sc system-ui blinkmacsystemfont neue sans gb yahei ui arial sans-serif border-box>从四足具身智能率先“上岗”，到人形机器人蓄势待发，中船动力集团正以务实之姿，稳步构建面向未来的智能工业新生态，为我国船舶工业高质量发展探索出一条可复制、可推广的智能化转型路径。</span></span></p></section></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section class="mp_profile_iframe_wrp"><mp-common-profile class="custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe mp_common_widget" data-pluginname="mpprofile" data-nickname="中船动力集团" data-from="0" data-headimg="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/vp6g9F7DuoTJMSxH8GiczpUMg3aI8KVCPLvmiaslJkVH35kXK7HlNvT03hOia6YiazXiatFI1rmxicQyicA03nAYUjXia5r2vLiaF67twydw1aqIrw2I/0?wx_fmt=png" data-signature="中国船舶集团有限公司旗下中船动力（集团）有限公司官方订阅号" data-id="Mzg3NjU0MTk3NA==" data-service_type="1" data-verify_status="2"></mp-common-profile></section><section style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.562962962962963" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" type="block" data-imgfileid="100022114" data-aistatus="1" style="height: auto !important; max-width: 600px" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/bGrTZK06u8RDDkSmHuTXGOPtWjibjlfXeTKfQshY9JP9OrpL9zcflZyibQ2wichoIoibWIuVDmKbiaT3kBE3bkU13Gw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></section></section><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="10000"></mp-style-type></p></div><video id="video" src="http://mpvideo.qpic.cn/0b2ezmcomaaeq4aj2x6lq5uvjs6d43fqjzqa.f10002.mp4?dis_k=c7f274fe459111f3cc64a85ed8a57dde&amp;dis_t=1775345811&amp;play_scene=10120&amp;auth_info=Wr+oqMIvSSl70/CejShiBD9XZktAPldwOWlQHjdhB2NhZFpoZQJSZAw/NU9ZR28kK10=&amp;auth_key=04b44930b8de5d21e1bf376d9fef207b" width="100%" controls><div class="fallback"><p></p></div></video><br><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/v_cc1nWR4bxXRvKYQ8uvBA" style="color: blue" class="media_tool_meta meta_primary">文章原文</a><br><div> 平台地址：<a href="http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/5adjp98wun">http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/5adjp98wun</a></div><img alt="" width="1px" height="1px" class="" style="width:1px;height:1px;display:none" src="http://www.jintiankansha.me/rss_static/133721/5adjp98wun"> ]]>
