            <title>
                <![CDATA[ 中船动力集团举办2026年第一期技术内训师能力提升培训班 ]]>
            </title>
            <link>http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3NjU0MTk3NA==&mid=2247536029&idx=2&sn=92c111f17715fdf9a69032c57b359da8&chksm=cf32ace4f84525f226e5ce498533135a8dc93dd248e8623e461f175fa48ad1459857e51a6205#rd</link>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[ 为打造一支师资数量更加充足、专业领域更加齐全、专业能力更加过硬、讲授水平更加突出的培训师队伍，为公司高质量发展赋能增势，3月27日至28日，中船动力集团举办2026年第一期技术内训师能力提升培训班。来自中船动力集团所属相关企业的四十位一线技术、技能骨干齐聚一堂，共同精进授课技能与专业素养。中船动力集... ]]>
            </description>
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[ <div class="rich_media_content" id="js_content"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);margin-bottom: 0px;"><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="line-height: 0;text-align: center;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.1361111111111111" data-s="300,640" data-w="1080" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important; max-width: 600px" data-aistatus="1" data-type="jpeg" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/vp6g9F7DuoRkJDkerCptWg04ZzicXxSINobsHposibKGHEgXR3g3xtjetRiavatUzgXN8B0RlARA9fdRVHkP0sjzRJ3hHmicvGAzo9Z6aHLB7hk/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></section></section></section><section style="margin: 15px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-indent: 2.125em;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">为打造一支师资数量更加充足、专业领域更加齐全、专业能力更加过硬、讲授水平更加突出的培训师队伍，为公司高质量发展赋能增势，3月27日至28日，中船动力集团举办2026年第一期技术内训师能力提升培训班。来自中船动力集团所属相关企业的四十位一线技术、技能骨干齐聚一堂，共同精进授课技能与专业素养。</span></p></section></section><section style="text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-aistatus="1" data-ratio="0.6276595744680851" data-s="300,640" data-w="846" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important; max-width: 600px" data-type="png" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/vp6g9F7DuoR1NnbB3egQ0NMbncgct3l8cmBdTMCY4J0f6eEvvHlygU6xZBRcvgsWfbH0BRwbutr1ria6C2p4gfFrx5A1eD6D2ibTsoChicicruM/640?wx_fmt=png"></section></section><section style="text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-indent: 2.125em;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">中船动力集团副总工程师、技术培训中心负责人周伟中出席开班仪式并作动员讲话，强调了提升内训师能力既是夯实内部技术梯队建设的关键举措，更是向客户传递专业价值、深化产业链协同的重要支撑。</span></p></section><section style="text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 51%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: stretch;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 18px;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 10px;height: 10px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;background-color: rgb(223, 16, 85);box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 18px;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 10px;height: 10px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;background-color: rgb(104, 199, 252);box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p></section></section></section></section></section><section style="text-align: center;margin: 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.7504302925989673" data-s="300,640" data-w="581" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important; max-width: 600px" data-aistatus="1" data-type="png" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/vp6g9F7DuoSKdnjWvVicicwoaXo39tvJuplUdpkFUFZJK79HpL901ibpBiboSjYaPdIyvlZ39aicPZdqZTHw5iaVQw7ibG3ViaFDHcJxWyCZptiaIZibk/640?wx_fmt=png"></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;align-self: stretch;flex: 100 100 0%;height: auto;padding: 0px 0px 0px 13px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 6px 0px 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="background-color: rgb(202, 202, 202);height: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;"><svg viewbox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section><section style="text-align: center;margin: 0px 0px 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.7512776831345827" data-s="300,640" data-w="587" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important; max-width: 600px" data-aistatus="1" data-type="png" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/vp6g9F7DuoR8OFJkuxIibj9mqZ7pd4YwoEmhicpQuJrQfeLKypqNkG4V0KqE2GNsjjicg1dbiaUtvibpfM9eD3DWVXwpjKptXPIibjNic3qavozbpc/640?wx_fmt=png"></section></section></section></section><section style="text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-indent: 2em;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">培训围绕“从会技术到善授课，从懂专业到能传播”的核心目标，设置了系统化、实战化的课程体系，内容涵盖授课表达技巧、课堂控场方法、学员注意力引导、课程吸引力打造、专业内容提炼及课程设计开发等关键环节。通过培训，参训学员熟练掌握了标准授课流程与课堂管理办法，语言表达逻辑与课堂呈现感染力得到提升，整体实现了从“技术、技能骨干”到“授课讲师”的初步跨越。</span></p></section><section style="text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.44562647754137114" data-s="300,640" data-w="846" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important; max-width: 600px" data-aistatus="1" data-type="png" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/vp6g9F7DuoRibIRiacZT7SdSnWmIib8AcFsicx0DCGkWXdAldFTsibsOI6FuaFtAw8UBSwQbXT4Tb3xo56zP9u64wmdRFvdlht5cs5fiaD03AiaGaw/640?wx_fmt=png"></section></section><section style="text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-indent: 2.125em;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="text-indent: 2em;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">本次培训是中船动力集团完善技术培训体系、提升品牌价值的一项重要举措，将为企业提升客户服务质量和水平、增强核心竞争力提供持续的支撑。</span></span></p></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section class="mp_profile_iframe_wrp"><mp-common-profile class="custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe mp_common_widget" data-pluginname="mpprofile" data-nickname="中船动力集团" data-from="0" data-headimg="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/vp6g9F7DuoTJMSxH8GiczpUMg3aI8KVCPLvmiaslJkVH35kXK7HlNvT03hOia6YiazXiatFI1rmxicQyicA03nAYUjXia5r2vLiaF67twydw1aqIrw2I/0?wx_fmt=png" data-signature="中国船舶集团有限公司旗下中船动力（集团）有限公司官方订阅号" data-id="Mzg3NjU0MTk3NA==" data-service_type="1" data-verify_status="2"></mp-common-profile></section><section style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.562962962962963" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" type="block" data-imgfileid="100022114" data-aistatus="1" style="height: auto !important; max-width: 600px" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/bGrTZK06u8RDDkSmHuTXGOPtWjibjlfXeTKfQshY9JP9OrpL9zcflZyibQ2wichoIoibWIuVDmKbiaT3kBE3bkU13Gw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></section></section><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="10000"></mp-style-type></p></div><br><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3NjU0MTk3NA==&amp;mid=2247536029&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=92c111f17715fdf9a69032c57b359da8&amp;chksm=cf32ace4f84525f226e5ce498533135a8dc93dd248e8623e461f175fa48ad1459857e51a6205#rd" style="color: blue" class="media_tool_meta meta_primary">文章原文</a><br><div> 平台地址：<a href="http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/kSragjP5UK">http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/kSragjP5UK</a></div><img alt="" width="1px" height="1px" class="" style="width:1px;height:1px;display:none" src="http://www.jintiankansha.me/rss_static/133721/kSragjP5UK"> ]]>
            </content:encoded>
