        <item>
            <title>
                <![CDATA[ 中船沪东重机低速机单月产量再创历史新高 ]]>
            </title>
            <link>http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/35cY32BSOth5s3sVJzsNZQ</link>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[ 春潮涌动，捷报频传。3月份，中船动力集团下属中船沪东重机低速机生产战线喜获丰收。一季度上海、镇江两地低速机生产同比增长21%，其中3月份单月产量创下历史新高；同时，镇江制造基地3月刷新了双燃料主机单月生产纪录。这份亮眼成绩单，既是生产系统攻坚克难的生动体现，更是中船动力集团深化精益管理、强化运营型管... ]]>
            </description>
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[ <div class="rich_media_content" id="js_content"><section style="background-color: rgb(242, 243, 245);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="line-height: 0;text-align: center;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-aistatus="1" data-ratio="0.1361111111111111" data-s="300,640" data-w="1080" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important; max-width: 600px" data-type="jpeg" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/vp6g9F7DuoRkJDkerCptWg04ZzicXxSINobsHposibKGHEgXR3g3xtjetRiavatUzgXN8B0RlARA9fdRVHkP0sjzRJ3hHmicvGAzo9Z6aHLB7hk/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></section></section></section><section style="text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 20px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px -2px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 102.996px;height: 5.99609px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;margin: 22px 0px 0px 9px;padding: 0px;background-color: rgb(254, 238, 225);box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 31px 0px 0px;transform: translate3d(11px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(11px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(11px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(11px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify;font-size: 30px;color: rgb(255, 20, 64);box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 55px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 95%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(74, 100, 174) 4px 4px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35) 0px 0px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 15px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.8;padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-indent: 2.2143em;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">春潮涌动，捷报频传。3月份，中船动力集团下属中船沪东重机低速机生产战线喜获丰收。一季度上海、镇江两地低速机生产同比增长21%，其中3月份单月产量创下历史新高；同时，镇江制造基地3月刷新了双燃料主机单月生产纪录。这份亮眼成绩单，既是生产系统攻坚克难的生动体现，更是中船动力集团深化精益管理、强化运营型管控的成果缩影。</span></p></section></section></section></section><section style="text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 15px 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 95%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;padding: 15px 20px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);height: auto;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.21) 1px 1px 6px 0px;border-radius: 5px;overflow: hidden;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-style: solid;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgb(228, 205, 167);box-shadow: rgb(144, 141, 141) 3px 3px 3px;box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-aistatus="1" data-ratio="0.6666666666666666" data-s="300,640" data-w="1080" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important; max-width: 600px" data-type="jpeg" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/vp6g9F7DuoQqeqZHKZUCyPQf2wNFltYfgzKfTgtuZ4oNydY63YbqdMme0PUNxv0xicuJkrDuqZwJvjHbQ6JeabVhqic053kHXVtPNMYOhVz94/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></section></section><section style="text-align: justify;line-height: 0.2;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p></section><section style="text-align: justify;line-height: 1.8;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-indent: 2.1333em;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">春节刚过，中船沪东重机便迅速进入“战斗”模式，紧扣提质增效核心目标，上海、镇江两地同频共振、协同攻坚。中船沪东重机上海本部深度推进精益排产、优化装配流程，压实生产节拍；镇江基地通过工艺优化、工序前移和五小创新，攻关双燃料主机痛点，持续优化双燃料主机台位周期，并在三个新建试车台上验证了一套辅机系统单月完成4台主机提交，一键备车功能效果显著，生产效率实现重大突破，为马年首季“月考”交出满意的答卷。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2.1333em;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">在“十五五”开局之际，中船沪东重机全面深化精益管理，依托运营型管控平台，构建起“计划—执行—反馈—改善”的闭环管理机制。通过细化节拍管理、强化供应链协同、推行标准化作业，产线综合效率显著提升。特别是在双燃料主机等重点产品上，生产、技术、质量、采购多部门协同作战，关键零部件供应保障率、装配效率和调试一次通过率均实现稳步提升，为产能持续释放筑牢根基。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2.1333em;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">中船沪东重机将继续锚定全年目标任务，深化精益管理实践，优化两地协同机制，以更高效的运营、更优质的产品，为中船动力集团高质量发展贡献更大力量。</span></span></p></section></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section class="mp_profile_iframe_wrp"><mp-common-profile class="custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe mp_common_widget" data-pluginname="mpprofile" data-nickname="中船动力集团" data-from="0" data-headimg="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/vp6g9F7DuoTJMSxH8GiczpUMg3aI8KVCPLvmiaslJkVH35kXK7HlNvT03hOia6YiazXiatFI1rmxicQyicA03nAYUjXia5r2vLiaF67twydw1aqIrw2I/0?wx_fmt=png" data-signature="中国船舶集团有限公司旗下中船动力（集团）有限公司官方订阅号" data-id="Mzg3NjU0MTk3NA==" data-service_type="1" data-verify_status="2"></mp-common-profile></section><section style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.562962962962963" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" type="block" data-imgfileid="100022114" data-aistatus="1" style="height: auto !important; max-width: 600px" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/bGrTZK06u8RDDkSmHuTXGOPtWjibjlfXeTKfQshY9JP9OrpL9zcflZyibQ2wichoIoibWIuVDmKbiaT3kBE3bkU13Gw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></section></section><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="10000"></mp-style-type></p></div><br><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/35cY32BSOth5s3sVJzsNZQ" style="color: blue" class="media_tool_meta meta_primary">文章原文</a><br><div> 平台地址：<a href="http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/KYGbZnhYjZ">http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/KYGbZnhYjZ</a></div><img alt="" width="1px" height="1px" class="" style="width:1px;height:1px;display:none" src="http://www.jintiankansha.me/rss_static/133721/KYGbZnhYjZ"> ]]>
            </content:encoded>
