加工变形问题，零件质量提高90%，获中船河柴“双五小”一等奖；优化主轴承盖加工工艺，节约加工时间50%，创效约10万元，多项改进实现效率与质量双提升。他坚持“以赛促学”，获2025年中船河柴技能竞赛加工中心项目第一名，获评“河柴技术标兵”。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">闫明东始终坚守一线，立志成为懂操作、会设计的复合型人才，用实干彰显新时代产业工人的匠心与担当。</span></p></section></section></section><section style="text-align: right;margin: -60px 0px 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 19%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="1.6040609" data-s="300,640" data-w="197" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 600px" width="100%" data-aistatus="1" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/2hNR2haicTHMPmjpnLNzHsd6UgSuibMOTGRZeeU0d8URnwhFk1EEjUvzA5iab19Am6vYRYQOia5xDjhgHZohngEHgBXJAicYynpvbCwDFTicIYvS8/640?wx_fmt=png"></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section style="text-align: right;justify-content: flex-end;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px -30px;transform: translate3d(-20px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-20px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-20px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-20px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;padding: 0px;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: left;margin: 5px 0px 0px;opacity: 1;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 20.9804px;height: 19.9674px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;background-color: rgb(239, 191, 138);border-radius: 20px;box-sizing: border-box;"><svg viewbox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg><