a-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" data-w="1080" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important; max-width: 600px" data-type="jpeg" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/vp6g9F7DuoQyolD7050YwU2EF1LrRw4JWGnrPHuJudkCnInobYdFjVCYRiadtuuCeMsz2dibjjXv45a5XAwVhnnSOR7bI1oDicZGhrOotUrc1c/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></section></section><section style="text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 92%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;padding: 20px;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;border-color: rgb(161, 24, 23);box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify;line-height: 2;padding: 0px;color: rgb(161, 24, 23);box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">中船河柴  郑晓臣</span></strong></p></section><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border-top: 1px dashed rgb(239, 191, 138);box-sizing: border-box;"><svg viewbox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section><section style="text-align: justify;font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px;color: rgb(161, 24, 23);box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">中船河柴总装高级工郑晓臣深耕柴油机装配、技术攻关与精益管理，立足岗位、勇挑重担，在重点型号研制、提质增效、创新创效及团队建设中表现突出</span></strong><strong style="text-indent: 2em;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="text-indent: 2em;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">。</span></span></strong></p></section><section style="text-align: justify;font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px;color: rgb(52, 54, 60);box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">他牵头完成重点产品推进样机装配任务，编制装配内控三检本，全程记录数据，累计解决各类问题百余项，保障首台柴油机装试顺利完成。负责重点项目发电机样机总装及可靠性鉴定试验现场管理，完成20余项改善，实现“零事故、零缺陷、高效率”目标，形成可复制推广的精益管理经验。参与CHD416V12、CHD416V16等机型装配，攻克共轨系统、进排气系统等装配难点，保障装配质量。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">他积极开展技术创新与精益改善，完成7项“五小”创新、4 项精益改善，参与3项QC课题攻关，其中《一种气缸盖吊装工具及方法》获专利受理。参与智能装配线效能提升科研项目，实现CHD622V20、TBD234V12线体装配效率分别提升11.5%、11%，达到预设目标。针对重点项目柴油机试验周期长、成本高问题，优化流程将单循环时长大幅缩短，节约费用百余万元，试验提前15天完成。</span></p></section></section></section><section style="text-align: right;margin: -60px 0px 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 19%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="1.6040609137055837" data-s="300,640" data-w="197" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important; max-width: 600px" data-aistatus="1" data-type="png" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/2hNR2haicTHMPmjpnLNzHsd6UgSuibMOTGRZeeU0d8URnwhFk1EEjUvzA5iab19Am6vYRYQOia5xDjhgHZohngEHgBXJAicYynpvbCwDFTicIYvS8/640?wx_fmt=png"></section></section><section class="mp_profile_iframe_wrp"><mp-common-profile class="custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe mp_common_widget" data-pluginname="mpprofile" data-nickname="中船动力" data-from="0" data-headimg="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/bGrTZK06u8SP8XJg2tezBcjUAdLarDxqoibPnCS46h8eRMb3NiauRdZPiav8Ldo1xve3d3GofcLDGyMfJE5ejVuSw/0?wx_fmt=png" data-signature="中国船舶集团有限公司旗下中船动力（集团）有限公司官方订阅号" data-id="Mzg3NjU0MTk3NA==" data-service_type="1" data-verify_status="2"></mp-common-profile></section><section style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-aistatus="1" data-imgfileid="100022114" data-ratio="0.562962962962963" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" type="block" style="height: auto !important; max-width: 600px" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/bGrTZK06u8RDDkSmHuTXGOPtWjibjlfXeTKfQshY9JP9OrpL9zcflZyibQ2wichoIoibWIuVDmKbiaT3kBE3bkU13Gw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></section></section><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="10000"></mp-style-type></p></div><br><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3NjU0MTk3NA==&amp;mid=2247535928&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=c8610fb3c2fe765bcac7f1b1b874eef9&amp;chksm=cf32ac41f845255714192a8944a872ac3488b59831d24e4a3b0dae1f2dd4fbbce5475966f610#rd" style="color: blue" class="media_tool_meta meta_primary">文章原文</a><br><div> 平台地址：<a href="http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/oWRO1rhcWU">http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/oWRO1rhcWU</a></div><img alt="" width="1px" height="1px" class="" style="width:1px;height:1px;display:none" src="http://www.jintiankansha.me/rss_static/133721/oWRO1rhcWU"> ]]>
